  <summary>10/8/1998--Introduced.
Homeowners' Emergency Mortgage Assistance Act - Directs the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to establish a mortgage emergency assistance program for qualifying homeowners with National Housing Act-insured mortgages who are unable to temporarily meet their obligations due to financial hardship beyond their control. Requires homeowner repayment of such assistance and interest.</summary>
